	Let me kindly inform you that Frontiers in Bioengineering and Biotechnology is now welcoming the submission of contributions to a Research Topic titled "Metagenomics profiling : advances in algorithmic approaches and biomedical applications" (http://journal.frontiersin.org/ResearchTopic/3144)

